N:omx
D:Multi-agent orchestration layer for Codex CLI. Provides 30 specialized agents, 40+ workflow skills, tmux team mode, persistent MCP servers, and a staged pipeline (plan->prd->exec->verify->fix).
G:omx multi-agent orchestration codex openai team-mode mcp-servers workflow

U[5]:
  Orchestrate complex multi-agent workflows (Codex CLI)
  Collaborate on large tasks via parallel tmux team workers
  Use persistent MCP servers for state, memory, and code intelligence
  Run staged pipeline (plan->prd->exec->verify->fix)
  Perform specialized work via role-based agent prompts
S[5]{n,action,details}:
  1,Install,npm install -g oh-my-codex && omx setup && omx doctor
  2,Launch,omx --xhigh --madmax (recommended; high reasoning + dangerously-bypass-approvals)
  3,Role Prompts,/prompts:architect "analyze..." / /prompts:executor "implement..." / /prompts:security-reviewer "audit..."
  4,Workflow Skills,$plan "$task" / $autopilot "$task" / $team 3:executor "$task" / $ulw (ultrawork)
  5,Team Mode,omx team 4:executor "$task" -> manage status/resume/shutdown
R[4]:
  Run omx doctor first for install/runtime diagnostics
  Follow staged pipeline order: plan->prd->exec->verify->fix
  Pre-verify team mode with omx doctor --team
  Persist state across sessions with MCP server omx_state
E[4]{desc,in,out}:
  "Install and initialize","npm install -g oh-my-codex && omx setup && omx doctor","OMX installed; prompts/skills/MCP configured"
  "Run team mode","omx team 4:executor 'fix all TypeScript errors'","4 parallel executor agents run concurrently in tmux"
  "Code review","$code-review (inside Codex)","Combined code review report from quality/security/api reviewers"
  "Autonomous execution","$autopilot 'implement user registration with email verification'","Automatically runs stages through plan->prd->exec->verify"
